    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Time Stop</strong> (Level 9 Transmutation)</p><p>You briefly stop the flow of time for everyone but yourself. No time passes for other creatures, while you take 1d4 + 1 turns in a row, during which you can use actions and move as normal.</p><p>This spell ends if one of the actions you use during this period, or any effects that you create during this period, affects a creature other than you or an object being worn or carried by someone other than you. In addition, the spell ends if you move to a place more than 1,000 feet from the location where you cast it.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Self | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Sorcerer, Wizard</em></p>",
